data.description: **SELLER HAS AN ASSUMABLE MORTGAGE with 2.75% interest rate for qualified buyer**Adorable lakefront 3/2 home in the highly desirable community of Sawgrass Lakes. Situated on an extra large corner lot with a fenced backyard and panoramic views of the lake. NEW roof, washer/dryer, refrigerator, & AC all in 2021. Home features split floor plan, stainless appliances, laminate flooring in main living areas, complete hurricane protection and a whole house water filtration/conditioning system! Barn doors open to extra den/office. Lower HOA fee includes lawn care, community pool, clubhouse, fitness center, billiard room, gate, basic cable & internet. Close to 95 and turnpike for easy commuting.
